## Modernization Goals

### Consolidation

Centralize data from multiple systems into a unified platform.

### Scalability

Support growing data volumes without major infrastructure redesign.

### Automation

Reduce manual operational effort through metadata-driven processing.

### Governance

Improve lineage, auditing, security, and data quality controls.

### Analytics Enablement

Provide trusted datasets for reporting, data science, and AI workloads.

